  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Phase 2, randomized, open-label study to evaluate vadadustat versus epoetin alfa
      for the treatment of anemia in subjects with DD-CKD who are hyporesponsive to ESAs.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
